name: RocketVerse
public_notice: RocketVerse (RKV) has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. Visit this Twitter post for more information and visit the old token page here.

description.en:
RocketVerse is a startup focused on developing a high-quality 3rd person shooter game with a self-sustaining economy integrated into the blockchain.

The RocketVerse universe basically consists of 3 utilities:
- RKV native token.
- Collectible, exclusive and in-game utility NFTs.
- FPS game RKV Arena.
